doc.after: A panoramic view of the city of Dar es Salaam Visible are the Bank of Tanzania twin towers the PPF Towers the Mafuta House and the Julius Nyerere Pension Tower to the right the Kariakoo area next with the Benjamin Mkapa National Stadium at the back followed by the slums
